description:
## Summary
The matchesAny helper function in extism_subscriber.go is trivial and can be eliminated using slices.ContainsFunc inline.

## Location
`internal/wasm/extism_subscriber.go:86-93`

## Current
```go
func (s *ExtismSubscriber) matchesAny(stream string, patterns []string) bool {
    for _, pattern := range patterns {
        if s.matchPattern(stream, pattern) {
            return true
        }
    }
    return false
}
```

## Proposed
```go
if \!slices.ContainsFunc(patterns, func(p string) bool {
    return s.matchPattern(event.Stream, p)
}) {
    continue
}
```

## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] Tests pass before change (baseline)
- [ ] Remove matchesAny and inline with slices.ContainsFunc
- [ ] All existing tests still pass
- [ ] Independent review by subagent confirms simplification maintains behavior
